title: The Reincarnation of the Forbidden Archmage
description: The Reincarnation of the Forbidden Archmage ManhwaOne day, dungeons suddenly appeared. Humans with awakened skills then set out to face these dungeons in search of hope and riches. Our protagonist, Saeki, having no skills, is considered incompetent; in order to earn enough money for the treatment of his little sister with an incurable disease, he decided to become an adventurer. Saeki has a secret, in his previous life he was the most powerful mage. Since his reincarnation he has to level up to regain his former powers. This is the story of an incompetent who will turn the world upside down with his power! Kinki no Tensei Daimadoushi The Reincarnation of the Forbidden Archmage 禁忌の転生大魔導士 ～無能からレベルアップで最強に～ 禁忌の転生大魔道士 Kinki no Tensei Daimadoushi ~Munou kara Level Up de Saikyou ni~
